\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

定义在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

的某个去心领域上, 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

处极限为
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的充要条件是
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x_{n}\to x_{0}$
\end_inset

, (
\begin_inset Formula $n\to\infty$
\end_inset

), 且
\begin_inset Formula $x_{n}\ne x_{0}$
\end_inset

, (
\begin_inset Formula $\forall n$
\end_inset

), 均有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{n\to\infty}f(x_{n})=A.
\]

